<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,358,923]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">
Size medium, 
<quantity box="[313,499,358,383]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.175" metricValueMax="10.05" metricValueMin="6.3" pageId="1" pageNumber="592" unit="mm" value="8.175" valueMax="10.05" valueMin="6.3">6.3 to 10.05 mm</quantity>
long. Color fuscous to piceous, forewings with ochraceous spots in membrane and veins with alternating dark and pale markings, sometimes with transverse, light brown subapical band or claval spot.
</paragraph>
